/* STREAMING_CHUNK: Adding a precision search-and-replace edit turn... */{"messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "I want to modify the scene where Julian meets Sister Clara in workspace/alpine-gothic/chapter-001.md. Instead of her holding an iron lantern, she should be carrying a collection of dried, black mountain mushrooms in a copper bowl, which will establish the fungal theme immediately."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "<tool_call>\n{"name": "read", "args": {"path": "workspace/alpine-gothic/chapter-001.md"}}\n</tool_call>"}, {"role": "user", "content": "System Tool Result:\n{"content": "# Chapter 1: The Ascent\n\nThe iron cable car hung suspended...\n\nWhen the cable car finally shuddered to a halt in the wooden docking bay, the silence of the high ridge rushed in to meet him. It was a heavy, suffocating silence, broken only by the rhythmic, mechanical sighing of the valley wind passing through the roof shingles. Sister Clara stood waiting on the wooden platform, her wool habit damp with condensation. She held an iron lantern, its yellow flame casting long, dancing shadows across her pale face. She did not smile as Julian stepped onto the wet planks; she merely looked at his medical bag with a quiet, knowing gaze."}"}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "<tool_call>\n{"name": "edit", "args": {"path": "workspace/alpine-gothic/chapter-001.md", "oldString": "Sister Clara stood waiting on the wooden platform, her wool habit damp with condensation. She held an iron lantern, its yellow flame casting long, dancing shadows across her pale face. She did not smile as Julian stepped onto the wet planks; she merely looked at his medical bag with a quiet, knowing gaze.", "newString": "Sister Clara stood waiting on the wooden platform, her wool habit damp with condensation. Instead of a lantern, she cradled a shallow copper bowl filled with dried, velvet-black mountain mushrooms that filled the cold air with a sharp, earthy decay. She did not smile as Julian stepped onto the wet planks; she merely looked at his medical bag and then down at the dark, shriveled specimens in her hands."}}\n</tool_call>"}, {"role": "user", "content": "System Tool Result:\n{"success": true}"}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "The scene has been surgically updated. Sister Clara now carries the copper bowl containing black mountain mushrooms, reinforcing the fungal theme from the very first encounter."}]}
